title: Teriyaki Boyz - Serious Japanese
description:
Serious Japanese is the second album released by Japanese hip-hop group Teriyaki Boyz. It is scheduled to be released on January 28, 2009 in Japan by Star Trak Entertainment. The album marks the first American release of a Japanese hip hop group by a major label.
